# Convex
# Note: convex/_generated/ is committed so Vercel (and any build
# environment without CONVEX_DEPLOY_KEY) can typecheck + build without
# running `convex codegen`. The Convex CLI guards against running
# codegen inside Vercel's build env — committing the output is the
# standard workaround. Regenerate locally with `npx convex codegen`
# after any schema.ts change.

